        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "): but since it is natural to suppose that the census began from the southern boundary of the Trans-Jordanic territory, which was the river Arnon, and since ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "the city that is in the midst of the ravine",
        "children": []
      },
      {
